<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Yakni ʋt ʋba talaia
 Chihowa a binili hoka,
 Kenan oke, hochihi̱fot
 Isht taloho̱wʋt e hieli;

[C1]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.

[V2]
 Holitopa ai oklu̱ha,
 Ai iti̱ hullo abilia,
 Ayoshoba yʋt iiksho,
 Klaist mi̱kot a binili hoke,

[C2]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.

[V3]
 Klaist pithaiyana moyumʋt
 Chihowa itikba ma antʋt
 Pi okcha̱ya he, pim ahnit,
 Ai isht pi anumpohonlishke,

[C3]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.

[V4]
 Na̱ pi Okchalinchi Klaist ma!
 Pim ai ashʋcheka puyuta
 Kashoffit ish pin taiyahlit,
 Kenan a̱ isht ish pi onashke,

[C4]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.

[V5]
 Shilombish Holitopa yʋt,
 Yʋmmak o̱ ai alotowa na
 Ayohbi, anuktanla mʋt
 Achintot, a mominchi hoke,

[C5]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.

[V6]
 Pi̱ nukha̱kló, pi apelá,
 Chu̱kʋsh himona pim ihi̱kbí;
 Kenan e pisa hi oka,
 Pi̱ hullot ish pim atahlashke,

[C6]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.

[V7]
 Ish a yʋmohmi pulla na,
 Kenan ʋba pin talaia ka,
 Na̱ yukpʋt chukowa hi ʋt,
 Pim ʋlhtaha kʋt aia̱hlashke,

[C7]
   Pi Kenan achukma,
   Yʋmmak o̱ ia hosh il a̱ya,
   Kenan yakni pi̱ holitopa
   Ona hi osh il a̱ya hoke.</lyrics>
<aka>Pi Kenan achukma, Canaan</aka>
